Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.81,0:23:48.18,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}对这胸中的光荣的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:52.16,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}沉重的负担
